title: Looking for duo *(silver or higher)/Ranked Team *(any)

embed.description: Create & discover new Champion builds/strategies, check your Summoner statistics and try our powerful LoL charts.

body:
Looking for someone to duo with. Best if silver or higher, and also for an active fun friendly non-rage induced ranked team (any rank). I'm silver 3... getting back to rank. Would be interested if anyone is also keen to add to have fun in some normal games. I have Skype and my IGN: Frostwolf77.  I play any lanes but adc. Pref top/mid...but enjoy jung/supp just as much.

So yeah.... here's a    {{item:2009}}

replies.body: Sure thing. I'll be happy to duo q and play normals. Add me, my ign is WQLFY.
